{"tid":2238884,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"標你有無？","createTime":"2020-10-11T13:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T10:41:50.000Z","uid":32051,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1080b5d6ba732312ff4de8f326cf17b9d76f0087","tid":2238884,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:15:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">標</span>記樂園<span class=\"red\">你有無</span>食過？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcpbNv5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcpbNv5.png&h=0e6f263d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛雜撈麵$48<br />\n5舊金錢肚（二胃）入門級牛雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3舊牛肺 滑捋捋又有氣管爽脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一大片牛膀（胰臟） 我知好多人唔中意食，但其實我覺得好入味，好食到五香<br />\n<br />\n3舊牛腸  好肥美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆肥膏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾條西生菜，算有誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟機一碟撈麵醬，有d紅蔥頭咁，咸咸地，特別過蠔油。有油香。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麵底好足，食完好飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深水埗黃店，唔中意中式麵可以去隔離任你點車仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60377e54748f7db9716127404473fbf22a22c7c","tid":2238884,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae0921ffa6339241ee178cb4a8c36b3964ce1fc","tid":2238884,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"價錢又公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215466919a27f3b9de1e5032ea78e38ab7b37ab7","tid":2238884,"uid":43126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"標記一定要叫埋嗰味嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a72c7bb693141f5dc1523d631